{"tid":1208681,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好學韓國農民呀，犯法架","createTime":"2019-06-12T10:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T10:08:35.000Z","uid":40139,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed0ccbde8cfaffb11cdf7b15cc270a397af33e20","tid":1208681,"uid":40139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:00:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千奇唔好學韓國農民呀，犯法架</span><br />\n<br />\n又係當年今日輕輕鬆時間<br />\n<br />\n韓農們就沒有放棄過肢體衝擊的行動，粗略觀察下他們當年使用過以下「招式」：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 使用削尖竹支、拆下鐵馬鐵支攻擊警察<br />\n<br />\n2. 戴上保鮮紙護眼，以雨傘抵抗胡椒噴劑<br />\n<br />\n3. 以滅火筒噴向警員<br />\n<br />\n4. 將鐵馬組成矩陣，衝擊警方防線<br />\n<br />\n5. 意圖推倒警車<br />\n<br />\n6. 奪走警方的盾牌<br />\n<br />\n7. 拆毀公物，衝破路障"},{"pid":"8078f8b5b5dd64af3e6ab5db47751bf1a02293f3","tid":1208681,"uid":40139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37e6ca15c855ffb48fad5ac6577b5714ee8af10a","tid":1208681,"uid":40139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec9ed363861c8584a20dda09475b8adc9a1784a6","tid":1208681,"uid":116398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:01:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e4049307fa09c7c72beb55351c73b5db10dabc67","tid":1208681,"uid":32691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"果時係肉搏戰<br />\n<br />\n依家企係度都比人打把<br />\n<br />\n差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4833ca9c0d6eb4bf60b510def0ea40c7503b13","tid":1208681,"uid":131551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e81abe58daf90c78309d50f29366a058a0688f","tid":1208681,"uid":85461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.godisageek.com/wp-content/uploads/south-park-phone-destroyer-2.